{"parentUuid":"59a0a277-e77d-4b33-9e8f-dbe84c0fbbb7","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/workspace","sessionId":"bdbc6603-10df-4d9f-82ca-9700a260a58c","version":"2.0.42","gitBranch":"","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_01B9UbbfpHa6XdJR88DdH98N","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Here are all the DNS records for datawizz.ai with explanations:\n\n## DNS Records for datawizz.ai\n\n### A Records (IPv4 Addresses)\n- **104.21.14.67**\n- **172.67.158.37**\n\nThese are IPv4 addresses where the domain points. Both IPs belong to Cloudflare's network, indicating the site is using Cloudflare as a CDN/proxy service.\n\n### AAAA Records (IPv6 Addresses)\n- **2606:4700:3036::6815:e43**\n- **2606:4700:3033::ac43:9e25**\n\nThese are IPv6 addresses, also part of Cloudflare's network, providing IPv6 connectivity for modern devices.\n\n### NS Records (Nameservers)\n- **bart.ns.cloudflare.com**\n- **lia.ns.cloudflare.com**\n\nThese are the authoritative nameservers for the domain, hosted by Cloudflare. They control all DNS records for datawizz.ai.\n\n### MX Records (Mail Servers)\n- **1 aspmx.l.google.com** (highest priority)\n- **5 alt1.aspmx.l.google.com**\n- **5 alt2.aspmx.l.google.com**\n- **10 alt3.aspmx.l.google.com**\n- **10 alt4.aspmx.l.google.com**\n\nThese configure email handling through Google Workspace (formerly G Suite). Lower numbers = higher priority, so aspmx.l.google.com is the primary mail server.\n\n### TXT Records\n1. **Google Site Verification**: `google-site-verification=HNs-M8XQYV_wbcSLABJ65iH9761kmeMto0N5ytd_M08`\n   - Proves ownership of the domain to Google services\n\n2. **SPF Record**: `v=spf1 include:dc-aa8e722993._spfm.datawizz.ai include:_spf.google.com ~all`\n   - Specifies authorized mail servers to prevent email spoofing\n   - Includes both a custom SPF macro and Google's mail servers\n   - `~all` means soft fail for unauthorized sources\n\n### SOA Record (Start of Authority)\n- **Primary NS**: bart.ns.cloudflare.com\n- **Admin email**: dns.cloudflare.com\n- **Serial**: 2392992790\n- **Refresh**: 10000 seconds\n- **Retry**: 2400 seconds\n- **Expire**: 604800 seconds (7 days)\n- **Minimum TTL**: 1800 seconds (30 minutes)\n\nThis defines the authoritative information about the DNS zone.\n\n### Summary\nThe domain is fully managed by **Cloudflare** for DNS and CDN services, uses **Google Workspace** for email, and has proper security configurations (SPF for email authentication and site verification)."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1603,"cache_read_input_tokens":15275,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1603,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":716,"service_tier":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CWs1yfi4A2w3o3ejH4e4b","type":"assistant","uuid":"bbc4ba90-b384-457c-a948-a13376a4620c","timestamp":"2026-01-06T23:48:00.418Z"}
